PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782195489
OL,3,CTwo arrests in connection with
OL,4,CNottingham Hospital Mortuary services
OL,6,FThe force said the men, aged 55 and
OL,7,F59, were detained on Monday, on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of misconduct in a public
OL,9,Foffice as part of Operation Perth, its
OL,10,Flarge-scale investigation into
OL,11,Fmaternity services at the Queen's
OL,12,FMedical Centre and City Hospital.
OL,14,FThe force said detectives had
OL,15,Fdiscovered alleged breaches of
OL,16,Fregulations in relation to the
OL,17,Fmanagement and operating practices of
OL,18,Fthe mortuary services, which are run
OL,19,Fby Nottingham University Hospitals.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782195489
OL,3,CTwo arrests in connection with
OL,4,CNottingham Hospital Mortuary services
OL,6,FThey relate to the Human Tissue Act,
OL,7,Fwhich regulates activities concerning
OL,8,Fthe removal, storage, use and disposal
OL,9,Fof human tissue.
OL,11,FDeputy Chief Constable Rob Griffin
OL,12,Fsaid: "We recognise this will be
OL,13,Fparticularly distressing for affected
OL,14,Ffamilies who are part of Operation
OL,15,FPerth.
OL,17,F"Extensive support remains available
OL,18,Fthrough the Operation Perth page on
OL,19,Fthe Nottinghamshire Police website."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782195489
OL,3,CTwo arrests in connection with
OL,4,CNottingham Hospital Mortuary services
OL,6,FOperation Perth was launched by
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police on April 2024
OL,8,Fand is running separately to the
OL,9,Findependent review of maternity
OL,10,Fservices, which is examining about
OL,11,F2,500 cases and is due to deliver its
OL,12,Ffindings on Wednesday, June 24.
OL,14,FAddressing families in the review, DCC
OL,15,FGriffin added: "We appreciate that
OL,16,Fthis development comes only a few days
OL,17,Fbefore the publication of the
OL,18,FIndependent Maternity Review, led by
OL,19,FDonna Ockenden, which will be an
OL,20,Fimportant but difficult time for
OL,21,FFamilies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782195489
OL,3,CTwo arrests in connection with
OL,4,CNottingham Hospital Mortuary services
OL,6,F"We have contacted the families who we
OL,7,Fhave already identified as being
OL,8,Fdirectly impacted by the issues
OL,9,Festablished within the NUH trust
OL,10,Fmortuaries.
OL,12,F"As the investigation progresses, we
OL,13,Fwill contact other families who have
OL,14,Fbeen directly affected as soon as they
OL,15,Fare identified."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
