CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782195489
OL,3,CTwo arrests in connection with
OL,4,CNottingham Hospital Mortuary services
OL,6,FAround 2,500 families and more than
OL,7,F800 members of staff have contributed
OL,8,Fto the Ockenden review into NUH, with
OL,9,Fthe organisation having already paid
OL,10,Fout millions of pounds in compensation
OL,11,Fand fines after being prosecuted for
OL,12,Fpoor care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
